def is_bowl_or_plate(item:item):
    symbol is_bowl_plate = is_bowl(item) or is_plate(item)
    return is_bowl_plate

def needs_washing(item:item):
    symbol dirty_item = is_bowl_or_plate(item) and dirty(item)
    return dirty_item

def has_dishwasher_d(item:item):
    symbol has_dish_dishwasher = exists dishwasher: item: 
        is_dishwasher(dishwasher) and inside(item, dishwasher)
    return has_dish_dishwasher

behavior find_dirty_items_needing_washing():
    body:
        foreach item: item:
            if is_bowl_or_plate(item) and not visited(item):
                observe(item, "Check if the item needs washing")
            assert visited(item) and not needs_washing(item) and not has_dishwasher_d(item)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        find_dirty_items_needing_washing()
